            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " case, fills a shape to add the focus ring around the shape."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Note that the focus ring may actually be drawn outside the view but will be clipped to any clipping superview or the window content view."
